{"tid":2183490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（2008年）習近平：行政、立法、司法三個機構互相理解、互相支持","createTime":"2020-09-01T03:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T16:22:08.000Z","uid":201464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f9a2f49d27b4f2d8455c23adc281ec45f1c921","tid":2183490,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:22:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DtIVP93G75s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDtIVP93G75s&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7jizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=4cda153f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DtIVP93G75s</a> <br />\n2008年7月7日，時任國家副主席、中央港澳工作協調小組組長習近平訪問香港，首次在香港公開發表他的「三權合作論」，提出「&hellip;&hellip;行政、立法、司法三個機構互相理解、互相支持，共同珍惜我們現在來之不易的香港繁榮穩定的大好局面&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"a4e98c084f95cfd6b521c98ac4843f48a36a0e17","tid":2183490,"uid":201031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"小學雞講完三權合作香港仲當香港有三權分立係咪傻左<br />\n支共魔爪出晒面當睇唔到？"},{"pid":"b05106baf8ddd7b9b6bd1b7a8b8977bc4ce2ce26","tid":2183490,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4e98c084f95cfd6b521c98ac4843f48a36a0e17","tid":2183490,"uid":201031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"小學雞講完三權合作香港仲當香港有三權分立係咪傻左<br />\n支共魔爪出晒面當睇唔到？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"只係依家全面實行啫"},{"pid":"e7ac5a11c6714dde647bd526b47f5a58476fe055","tid":2183490,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b05106baf8ddd7b9b6bd1b7a8b8977bc4ce2ce26","tid":2183490,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4e98c084f95cfd6b521c98ac4843f48a36a0e17","tid":2183490,"uid":201031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"小學雞講完三權合作香港仲當香港有三權分立係咪傻左<br />\n支共魔爪出晒面當睇唔到？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"只係依家全面實行啫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"香港人唔係想支共有咁醜得咁醜咩<br />\n而家又幫港共講